  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "With the development and rise of EVM focused programming languages - besides Vyper and Solidity - like [Fe](https://github.com/ethereum/fe) and [Sway](https://sezna.github.io/EthCC-2021/) I think we should make it as easy as possible to make dapptools-rs accessible for these languages. \r\n\r\nI don't have enough knowledge at the moment to assess if this is already possible or how big the effort would be to make the integration as easy as possible for future languages.",
